gov.usgs.anss.util

Class GombergPacket

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.anss.util.GombergPacket

  • public class GombergPacket
extends java.lang.Object
    GombergPacket.java This object is designed to represent a USNSN gomberg packet (communications packet). The basic data is decoded into this packet and converstion from raw bytes to a GombergPacket and from a GombergPacket to Raw bytes is provided. Created on July 30, 2003, 9:24 AM
